metadata.name: Demons by Daylight
metadata.description:
1023 40th Light.

We are all being allowed to return to our homes. The damage done by the Six is being reversed, the true magic users have assumed power, but they reassure us our lives need not change. I can only imagine the pain of those who lost loved ones in the cataclysm. Everything looks similar to how it did just a week ago, but it feels so different. I see shadows dancing in the corner of my eyes. There are no conversations unheard by magic users. We may be safe, but we are not free. 
Part 3.
